<note n="0283002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283002">答＋（曰）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0283003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283003">伎＝技【明】</note>
<note n="0283004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283004">用＋（者）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0283005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283005">眾世所言∞此中應說【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0283006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283006">眾世所言∞此中應說【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0283007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283007">後＋（後）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0283008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0283008">隥＝蹬【宋】【元】，燈【宮】</note>
<note n="0284001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284001">彼＝後【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0284002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0284002">除＋（前）【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0285001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0285001">〔緣〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0286001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286001">有＝者【宮】</note>
<note n="0286002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286002">彼＋（或）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0286003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286003">障＋（或不礙）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0286004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286004">與＝無【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0286005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286005">〔苦〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0287001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287001">〔說〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0287002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0287002">惑＝或【三】【宮】＊</note>
